Package: rorpy
Type: Package
Title: R or Python? Simple Classification of Webpages by Code Content
Version: 0.1
Depends: R (>= 3.0.0)
Imports: randomForest, rvest, stringr, tibble, xml2
Author: Alastair Rushworth
Maintainer: Alastair Rushworth <alastairmrushworth@gmail.com>
Description: Classify whether a webpage contains R or Python code.  Uses a simple pre-trained classifier to assess whether html content tagged 'pre' and 'code' looks like R, Python or another language.
License: GPL-2
LazyLoad: yes
ByteCompile: yes
Suggests: testthat
